---
const highlights = [
  {
    title: 'Tech Innovation',
    description: 'I love exploring new technologies and finding creative ways to solve problems that actually matter.',
    icon: 'code'
  },
  {
    title: 'HomeLab Magic',
    description: 'My home lab is where I test, break, and perfect everything before it goes into production.',
    icon: 'server'
  },
  {
    title: 'Automation Obsessed',
    description: 'If I have to do something more than twice, I probably write a script to do it for me.',
    icon: 'zap'
  },
  {
    title: 'Knowledge Sharing',
    description: 'I believe the best way to learn is to teach, so I share what I discover along the way.',
    icon: 'heart'
  }
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-slate-800/50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        What I am <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400">About</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        I am someone who gets excited about making technology work better, whether it is in my home lab or helping others solve their tech challenges.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Hey there! I am Domi, and I have been tinkering with technology for as long as I can remember. 
          What started as curiosity about how things work has turned into a career of building systems 
          that actually solve real problems.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          My home lab is where the magic happens â€“ it is my playground for testing new ideas and learning 
          technologies before they hit the mainstream. I believe the best way to understand something is 
          to break it, fix it, and make it better.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          When I am not deep in server configurations or automation scripts, I enjoy sharing what I have learned 
          and helping others navigate their own tech journeys. There is nothing quite like that moment when 
          everything clicks and just works.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-700/50 to-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-600/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">In a nutshell</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>HomeLab tinkerer & problem solver</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>Automation enthusiast</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>Open source contributor</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
              <span>Always learning something new</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      {highlights.map((highlight) => (
        <div class="bg-slate-800/30 p-6 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/20 hover:border-slate-600/40 group">
          <div class="mb-4">
            {highlight.icon === 'code' && (
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            )}
            {highlight.icon === 'server' && (
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01"/>
              </svg>
            )}
            {highlight.icon === 'zap' && (
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            )}
            {highlight.icon === 'heart' && (
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 group-hover:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
              </svg>
            )}
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-400">
            {highlight.title}
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            {highlight.description}
          </p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>